915:\begin{lemma}[$\toBiprod$ explicit elementwise formula (iter-023)]
929:  Direct mirror of Mathlib's $\mathtt{toBiprod\_apply}$ (\texttt{MayerVietoris.lean} L48--64). The proof bridges via $(\AddCommGrpCat.\mathtt{biprodIsoProd}).\mathtt{addCommGroupIsoToAddEquiv}$'s injectivity, then $\mathtt{ext}$ on the two biproduct components, then closes each side by the $\mathtt{biprodIsoProd}$-vs-$\mathtt{biprod.lift}$ identities. Every step is value-category-agnostic and transfers cleanly. Plan-agent \texttt{lean\_run\_code} probe (iter-023) confirms the body typechecks end-to-end, kernel-only axioms.
