946:  Direct mirror of Mathlib's $\mathtt{fromBiprod\_biprodIsoProd\_inv\_apply}$ (\texttt{MayerVietoris.lean} L77--83). The body is a one-liner: \lstinline{dsimp [HModule'_fromBiprod]; rw [← ConcreteCategory.comp_apply]; simp [AddCommGrpCat.biprodIsoProd_inv_comp_desc, sub_eq_add_neg]}. Plan-agent \texttt{lean\_run\_code} probe (iter-023) confirms.
949:\begin{lemma}[$\Ext$-side / $\AddCommGrpCat$-side bridge for $\toBiprod$ (iter-023)]
963:  Direct mirror of Mathlib's $\mathtt{biprodAddEquiv\_symm\_biprodIsoProd\_hom\_toBiprod\_apply}$ (\texttt{MayerVietoris.lean} L85--91). Body: \lstinline{Ext.biprodAddEquiv.injective (by cat_disch)}. Requires the wrapper attributes $\mathtt{set\_option}$ \lstinline{backward.isDefEq.respectTransparency false in} (relaxes typeclass-search transparency, mirrors Mathlib L85) followed by $\mathtt{attribute}$ \lstinline{[local simp] HModule'_toBiprod_apply in} (registers Lemma~\ref{lem:Scheme_HModule_prime_toBiprod_apply} as a local $\mathtt{simp}$ lemma so $\mathtt{cat\_disch}$ can use it, mirrors Mathlib L86). Plan-agent \texttt{lean\_run\_code} probe (iter-023) confirms.
966:\begin{lemma}[$\Ext$-side / $\AddCommGrpCat$-side bridge for $\fromBiprod$ (iter-023)]
980:  Direct mirror of Mathlib's $\mathtt{mk_0\_f\_comp\_biprodAddEquiv\_symm\_biprodIsoProd\_hom}$ (\texttt{MayerVietoris.lean} L93--106). Body: \lstinline{obtain ⟨⟨x₂, x₃⟩, rfl⟩ := (AddCommGrpCat.biprodIsoProd _ _).addCommGroupIsoToAddEquiv.symm.surjective x; dsimp; rw [Ext.biprodAddEquiv_symm_apply, Iso.addCommGroupIsoToAddEquiv_symm_apply, HModule'_fromBiprod_biprodIsoProd_inv_apply]; cat_disch}. Requires the wrapper attributes $\mathtt{set\_option}$ \lstinline{backward.isDefEq.respectTransparency false in} (mirrors Mathlib L93) and $\mathtt{attribute}$ \lstinline{[local simp] sub_eq_add_neg in} (registers $\mathtt{sub\_eq\_add\_neg}$ as a local $\mathtt{simp}$ lemma to close the additive-inverse step, mirrors Mathlib L94). Plan-agent \texttt{lean\_run\_code} probe (iter-023) confirms.
